Description: Embrace Zerotox Handmade Body Wash Rose & Honey for a clean, fresh and fragrant bath every time. It contains essential ingredients like Rose, Honey, Azadirachta indica (Neem), Ananas comosus (Pineapple), Aloe vera, Crocus sativus (Saffron/Kesar), Curcuma aromatic (Wild Turmeric) along with Geranium Oil. Both Honey and Rose are unarguably unequalled for skin care making this body wash antibacterial, antiviral, anti-inflammatory, antifungal and enriched with antioxidants. The body wash is vegan as it is made with pure vegetable oil which accentuates the skin���s potency to retain moisture. As the name suggests Zerotox natural loofah is a wonderful exfoliating sponge that gently removes the surface layer of dead skin cells, leaving a radiant looking, healthy, and smooth skin. Along with this natural process of exfoliation, scrubbing your skin with natural loofah with gentle friction brushes off excess dead skin cells from the surface of your skin. Removing dead skin cells not only improves the look of your skin but also sweeps away places where bacteria and soil could collect. This enhances blood circulation, removes calluses, and helps to prevent ingrown hairs on the face and body. This long and fibrous bath accessory or natural loofah is procured from a plant resource. It is a product of the Xylocarpus Granatum Koen tree and bears a close resemblance to the cucumber fruit. When dried, the fruit leaves behind a durable fibre network. This fruit, after treating and drying results into a mildly abrasive scrubber that helps exfoliate your skin naturally and enhances skin surface circulation.
